Data Taking Statistics
Week of 2003 January 6-12
page.enlisting:

page.normal_text:
Major Sources of Downtime: Not recording during a store
Major Sources of Downtime: Not recording during a store
page.enlisting:
• Most problems above added 50-100% additional losses due to run pauses, readout crate front-end busies, L2/L3 disables, SCL inits, etc. – L2 CAL solved by power cycling crate – L1 Muon LV PS will be repaired or replaced during shutdown – Tracking Triggers – procedural error • ~0.5 hr: 30 Run transitions (~1 minute/per) • ~1.0 hr: 9 Begin or End Store transitions (~5 minutes/per) • ~1-2 hrs: Average 2-4% FEB during physics data taking – See next slide • Most problems above added 50-100% additional losses due to run
